WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:02:43.785 --> 00:02:46.988
I sense you. brother.

3
00:02:52.937 --> 00:02:54.271
Hiding...

4
00:02:57.354 --> 00:02:59.354
...behind your cloak.

5
00:03:01.812 --> 00:03:04.104
It is time to earn yours.

6
00:03:15.896 --> 00:03:17.812
Still too small to take me head on.

7
00:03:18.104 --> 00:03:19.062
Use the cave!

8
00:03:33.687 --> 00:03:35.146
You fight with rage.

9
00:03:35.521 --> 00:03:37.354
I fight like father.

10
00:03:38.521 --> 00:03:41.812
You are not father. you are Dek!

11
00:04:34.479 --> 00:04:35.812
Do you yield?

12
00:04:36.062 --> 00:04:37.104
Never!

13
00:04:37.896 --> 00:04:39.146
Good.

14
00:05:07.729 --> 00:05:10.646
I'm still alive. brother.

15
00:05:12.229 --> 00:05:15.062
Still much to prove...

16
00:05:15.146 --> 00:05:17.646
...to show who you are.

17
00:05:18.146 --> 00:05:20.604
I am Yautja.

18
00:05:22.021 --> 00:05:24.229
Not yet.

19
00:05:26.646 --> 00:05:28.812
Are you holding your sword. Kwei?

20
00:05:30.062 --> 00:05:31.687
No.

21
00:05:31.896 --> 00:05:33.062
Pick it up!

22
00:06:02.562 --> 00:06:05.021
You kept this toy?!

23
00:06:05.479 --> 00:06:08.354
You remember what happened...

24
00:06:09.312 --> 00:06:12.229
I lost my fang!

25
00:06:13.271 --> 00:06:16.687
And you saved my life.

26
00:06:17.437 --> 00:06:20.021
You protected me.

27
00:06:20.729 --> 00:06:21.979
Come here.

28
00:06:30.062 --> 00:06:32.145
Fixed it for you.

29
00:06:35.437 --> 00:06:37.729
Don't blow yourself up.

30
00:06:47.021 --> 00:06:50.604
Today you make a vow...

31
00:06:55.870 --> 00:06:59.273
...as our ancestors did before you.

32
00:06:59.771 --> 00:07:03.021
To earn your place in the clan...

33
00:07:03.354 --> 00:07:05.646
...you must choose your prey.

34
00:07:07.146 --> 00:07:09.146
Bring it home...

35
00:07:10.354 --> 00:07:13.021
...or never return.

36
00:07:20.562 --> 00:07:22.437
Wait - Go back!

37
00:07:26.646 --> 00:07:28.187
Genna.

38
00:07:28.562 --> 00:07:30.687
The death planet.

39
00:07:31.896 --> 00:07:35.562
Home of the un-killable Kalisk.

40
00:07:38.780 --> 00:07:41.950
Even father fears it.

41
00:07:43.229 --> 00:07:46.354
Then the Kalisk shall be my trophy.

42
00:07:46.896 --> 00:07:49.479
Father calls me the weakest...

43
00:07:50.437 --> 00:07:53.771
...so I must kill the strongest.

44
00:07:54.729 --> 00:07:57.271
Failure means death.

45
00:07:58.979 --> 00:08:02.021
Then I will not fail.

46
00:08:02.646 --> 00:08:04.812
I cannot allow it.

47
00:08:08.771 --> 00:08:10.437
I make my vow.

48
00:08:13.021 --> 00:08:15.562
I make my vow!

49
00:09:11.062 --> 00:09:11.896
Father.

50
00:09:13.396 --> 00:09:16.896
I welcome you with honor.

51
00:09:28.771 --> 00:09:31.896
Why is it not done?

52
00:09:32.729 --> 00:09:35.312
He deserves a hunt.

53
00:09:37.062 --> 00:09:40.104
He is our clan's weakness...

54
00:09:41.437 --> 00:09:43.812
...weakness must be culled.

55
00:09:44.854 --> 00:09:47.812
He will bring home the Kalisk.

56
00:09:49.854 --> 00:09:51.396
Foolishness.

57
00:09:51.479 --> 00:09:53.521
He is a runt.

58
00:09:54.021 --> 00:09:57.896
You should have done it as he slept.

59
00:09:58.604 --> 00:09:59.687
Kill him!

60
00:10:00.562 --> 00:10:01.396
Now!

61
00:10:11.812 --> 00:10:14.729
He will only honor us in death.

62
00:10:30.396 --> 00:10:31.771
Father.

63
00:10:44.187 --> 00:10:45.687
Kwei?

64
00:10:46.562 --> 00:10:48.979
Be brave. brother.

65
00:11:38.979 --> 00:11:40.062
Father!

66
00:11:50.521 --> 00:11:51.646
Kwei!!!

67
00:12:04.854 --> 00:12:08.062
To forgive weakness...

68
00:12:09.562 --> 00:12:11.937
...is to show weakness.

69
00:12:13.937 --> 00:12:15.729
No! Father. no!

70
00:12:23.812 --> 00:12:25.521
Get your sword!

71
00:12:28.604 --> 00:12:29.812
Kwei!!!

72
00:12:43.151 --> 00:12:45.954
COMPUTER. IN YAUTJA:
Launch sequence initiated.

73
00:12:56.062 --> 00:12:58.562
Bring it home.

74
00:16:00.812 --> 00:16:02.854
Bring it home.

75
00:16:05.354 --> 00:16:07.396
For Kwei.

76
00:21:44.758 --> 00:21:45.959
Yautja!

77
00:21:48.328 --> 00:21:50.698
Yautja!

78
00:22:04.311 --> 00:22:06.880
Is this... Is this... Is this...

79
00:22:06.980 --> 00:22:08.048
Is this better?

80
00:22:09.783 --> 00:22:11.519
Universal translation.

81
00:22:11.619 --> 00:22:14.154
You hear Yautja.
others hear their language...

82
00:22:15.789 --> 00:22:17.725
Oh. boy.

83
00:22:18.659 --> 00:22:20.193
This isn't great for you.

84
00:22:40.914 --> 00:22:43.283
It waits for the needles
to paralyze you.

85
00:22:44.317 --> 00:22:47.054
Then eats you
while you can't move.

86
00:22:54.194 --> 00:22:58.532
I could help you. but...
I need a hand.

87
00:23:05.405 --> 00:23:07.729
Yautja hunt alone.

88
00:23:07.741 --> 00:23:11.779
Yautja might hunt alone.
but they die alone too.

89
00:23:14.982 --> 00:23:17.250
Kalisk.

90
00:23:19.853 --> 00:23:22.590
You're hunting the Kalisk.

91
00:23:34.535 --> 00:23:36.269
Gotta run faster.

92
00:23:43.443 --> 00:23:45.212
It happens fast. huh?

93
00:23:46.980 --> 00:23:49.950
If you had a weapon.
you know. I could use it.

94
00:23:53.987 --> 00:23:56.189
Throw me that.
and I can get you the antidote.

95
00:23:58.726 --> 00:24:00.127
Now or never.

96
00:24:37.698 --> 00:24:39.833
Hi.

97
00:25:02.022 --> 00:25:04.291
Should be good as new.

98
00:25:09.462 --> 00:25:11.131
The venom makes them bloom.

99
00:25:11.231 --> 00:25:13.500
Also makes them
a handy antidote.

100
00:25:20.073 --> 00:25:21.709
How about a lift?

101
00:25:24.945 --> 00:25:26.780
Let's go.

102
00:25:30.618 --> 00:25:32.252
Excuse you. sir.

103
00:25:33.187 --> 00:25:35.396
What happened to your legs?

104
00:25:35.455 --> 00:25:37.490
I'm synthetic.
I was built and deployed

105
00:25:37.591 --> 00:25:40.327
by the Weyland-Yutani
Corporation for research.

106
00:25:40.427 --> 00:25:42.963
Because their humans wouldn't
last a day on this planet.

107
00:25:43.063 --> 00:25:44.197
We found that...

108
00:25:50.938 --> 00:25:52.906
Look...

109
00:25:53.006 --> 00:25:56.176
Many Yautja have come
for the great Kalisk.

110
00:25:56.276 --> 00:25:58.646
and none have survived it...

111
00:25:58.746 --> 00:26:00.147
or Genna.

112
00:26:03.283 --> 00:26:05.185
I've seen the Kalisk.

113
00:26:05.719 --> 00:26:07.320
I survived it.

114
00:26:08.455 --> 00:26:11.224
Here's my proposal:
You take me along with you.

115
00:26:11.324 --> 00:26:13.827
and I'll guide you to its den.

116
00:26:13.927 --> 00:26:16.296
Once there. I get my legs.

117
00:26:16.396 --> 00:26:18.031
you get your trophy.

118
00:26:18.131 --> 00:26:21.268
and everyone's a winner. Deal?

119
00:26:23.687 --> 00:26:26.021
You have seen the Kalisk?

120
00:26:27.074 --> 00:26:31.144
Oh. yeah. I've seen the Kalisk.

121
00:26:42.923 --> 00:26:44.357
Okay. Hmm.

122
00:26:47.828 --> 00:26:49.596
Good luck with your journey.

123
00:26:50.798 --> 00:26:54.835
I'm just gonna...
go on my journey.

124
00:26:56.904 --> 00:26:58.939
I'm sure
you'll figure something out.

125
00:27:05.779 --> 00:27:08.515
Hey.

126
00:27:09.783 --> 00:27:12.853
I've already shown you
that I can be useful to you.

127
00:27:14.396 --> 00:27:16.271
Useful...

128
00:27:16.354 --> 00:27:17.979
like tool?

129
00:27:18.759 --> 00:27:22.763
Yes. Yes. exactly. like a tool.

130
00:27:22.863 --> 00:27:25.365
The only way to survive Genna
is to work with it.

131
00:27:25.465 --> 00:27:27.200
and I know how.

132
00:27:27.300 --> 00:27:30.437
And with the right tool...

133
00:27:31.905 --> 00:27:33.741
...you could get the Kalisk.

134
00:27:34.541 --> 00:27:35.909
You could be the first.

135
00:27:38.146 --> 00:27:40.604
I will use you. tool.

136
00:27:41.248 --> 00:27:43.650
You may call me Thi...
Whoa!

137
00:27:44.752 --> 00:27:48.889
You seem smaller than the other
Yautja. How old are you?

138
00:27:50.190 --> 00:27:51.759
And what does the chewing?

139
00:27:51.859 --> 00:27:54.327
Your outside fangs
or your inside teeth?

140
00:27:55.996 --> 00:27:58.598
Oh. What should I call you?

141
00:28:04.571 --> 00:28:06.439
Whoa!

142
00:28:06.539 --> 00:28:09.342
I've never been thrown before.
What a... ...thrill!

143
00:28:09.442 --> 00:28:11.678
How fast were you going
when your ship crashed?

144
00:28:11.779 --> 00:28:15.115
Faster than sub-light speed?
We haven't cracked that yet.

145
00:28:15.215 --> 00:28:17.484
Also. that plasma sword
is interesting.

146
00:28:17.584 --> 00:28:18.986
Is it unique to your clan?

147
00:28:19.086 --> 00:28:20.387
And what may I call you?

148
00:28:21.454 --> 00:28:24.324
I call these imbre anguis.

149
00:28:36.203 --> 00:28:37.871
They just want a snack.

150
00:28:45.212 --> 00:28:48.315
You catch more flies with honey
than you do with vinegar.

151
00:28:50.271 --> 00:28:51.604
Don't want flies.

152
00:28:52.052 --> 00:28:55.889
Predatory organisms are
my specific area of expertise.

153
00:28:55.989 --> 00:28:59.326
I've studied Yautja extensively.
It's an impressive culture.

154
00:29:00.961 --> 00:29:02.930
Here. ask me anything.
I bet I have the answer.

155
00:29:03.030 --> 00:29:04.464
Oh!

156
00:29:05.866 --> 00:29:07.267
Very funny.

157
00:29:07.367 --> 00:29:09.102
And you still haven't
told me your name.

158
00:29:30.646 --> 00:29:32.396
Name is Dek.

159
00:29:33.396 --> 00:29:35.187
Now talk that way.

160
00:29:35.195 --> 00:29:37.064
Okay. sure.

161
00:29:37.664 --> 00:29:41.835
Well. let's back up
and start at the beginning.

162
00:29:42.202 --> 00:29:45.272
Genna was formed
64 billion cycles ago.

163
00:29:45.372 --> 00:29:48.308
when a dying red dwarf star
in a neighboring system...

164
00:30:01.088 --> 00:30:03.123
It's so beautiful.

165
00:30:03.690 --> 00:30:06.259
After all the time
I've been stuck here.

166
00:30:06.359 --> 00:30:08.428
I never get tired of the view.

167
00:30:09.479 --> 00:30:12.187
How long have you been here?

168
00:30:12.199 --> 00:30:15.802
Well. we arrived on Genna two
years ago. and we built a base.

169
00:30:15.903 --> 00:30:18.405
Then. I was in
the vulture's nest

170
00:30:18.505 --> 00:30:20.240
for the most exciting

171
00:30:20.340 --> 00:30:23.476
13 days. seven hours. 43 minutes

172
00:30:23.576 --> 00:30:25.445
and two seconds of my life.

173
00:30:27.114 --> 00:30:29.082
But I always knew
someone would come.

174
00:30:30.083 --> 00:30:32.419
I was just wrong about who.

175
00:30:33.937 --> 00:30:35.771
Who would come?

176
00:30:39.026 --> 00:30:40.393
Tessa.

177
00:30:41.895 --> 00:30:45.432
Our crew is made up
entirely of synths.

178
00:30:45.532 --> 00:30:47.400
But Tessa and I are special.

179
00:30:48.001 --> 00:30:50.403
We have a higher sensitivity
than the others.

180
00:30:50.729 --> 00:30:53.604
Sensitivity is weakness.

181
00:30:56.276 --> 00:30:58.445
Sensitivity is what allows us
to understand

182
00:30:58.545 --> 00:31:00.447
the creatures on this planet.

183
00:31:04.117 --> 00:31:06.353
We were created
to work in tandem.

184
00:31:07.154 --> 00:31:11.158
Me. cooped up in the lab.
Tessa out in the field.

185
00:31:11.258 --> 00:31:14.594
Until the wonderful day
Tessa let me come with her.

186
00:31:14.694 --> 00:31:16.930
We were exploring Genna.

187
00:31:18.298 --> 00:31:21.434
And then the Kalisk attacked us.

188
00:31:22.535 --> 00:31:26.006
Separated me... and us.

189
00:31:28.608 --> 00:31:31.644
The last sound
I remember hearing

190
00:31:31.744 --> 00:31:35.115
was Tessa calling out my name.

191
00:31:35.782 --> 00:31:37.450
Reaching for me.

192
00:31:39.252 --> 00:31:41.054
Then the Kalisk.

193
00:31:42.255 --> 00:31:43.957
I didn't know what to do.

194
00:31:55.135 --> 00:31:57.804
But I refuse
to believe she's dead.

195
00:32:33.506 --> 00:32:35.508
Thia. Thia. Thia. Thia.

196
00:32:36.543 --> 00:32:38.978
Thia. Thia. Thia...

197
00:32:39.746 --> 00:32:42.015
Tessa!

198
00:32:43.483 --> 00:32:45.852
Thia. Thia. Thia. Thia.

199
00:32:45.952 --> 00:32:47.354
Thia. Thia.

200
00:33:26.926 --> 00:33:28.895
Hello. Tessa.

201
00:33:28.995 --> 00:33:31.664
The Company is not pleased.

202
00:33:33.466 --> 00:33:36.869
Continued failure will result
in your decommission.

203
00:33:40.407 --> 00:33:42.242
Where's Thia?

204
00:33:45.545 --> 00:33:47.514
The Yautja has Thia.

205
00:33:58.625 --> 00:34:00.979
I must eat.

206
00:34:00.993 --> 00:34:04.030
Two warriors.
Dek and Thia. on the hunt.

207
00:34:04.631 --> 00:34:06.099
Oh.

208
00:34:06.199 --> 00:34:07.867
Quick question.

209
00:34:07.967 --> 00:34:09.269
What should I be doing?

210
00:34:13.479 --> 00:34:15.521
What is this creature?

211
00:34:16.909 --> 00:34:19.479
Bone bison.
They're Kalisk food.

212
00:34:21.248 --> 00:34:24.854
Then it will be my food. too.

213
00:34:24.884 --> 00:34:28.255
So exciting.
Hunting with a Yautja.

214
00:34:28.355 --> 00:34:29.389
Tessa wouldn't believe it.

215
00:34:31.958 --> 00:34:33.226
Just a warning...

216
00:34:33.354 --> 00:34:34.979
Quiet tool!

217
00:34:38.398 --> 00:34:39.399
Razor grass.

218
00:34:43.035 --> 00:34:45.872
It'll cut you to ribbons.
We'll just go around.

219
00:34:48.771 --> 00:34:51.062
You give up too easily.

220
00:34:55.047 --> 00:34:57.350
We might not be alone
in this hunt.

221
00:35:07.627 --> 00:35:09.028
What an odd critter.

222
00:35:09.128 --> 00:35:11.164
I've never seen you before.

223
00:35:16.669 --> 00:35:18.638
Thia. Nice to meet you.

224
00:35:33.986 --> 00:35:35.522
Looks like your competition is better...

225
00:35:53.340 --> 00:35:55.975
Careful up in these trees.
There are Luna bugs!

226
00:36:17.196 --> 00:36:18.531
Coming up behind you!

227
00:36:32.211 --> 00:36:33.613
Stronger than it looks!

228
00:36:43.623 --> 00:36:46.493
Uh. Dek?

229
00:36:46.593 --> 00:36:49.095
Dek! Look!

230
00:37:33.373 --> 00:37:34.521
Kalisk?

231
00:37:34.541 --> 00:37:35.808
Not a Kalisk.

232
00:37:38.010 --> 00:37:40.112
This is a Luna bug!

233
00:37:48.120 --> 00:37:49.522
Have any other weapons?

234
00:38:46.479 --> 00:38:48.515
Why'd you stop?
Let's get out of here.

235
00:38:49.062 --> 00:38:50.937
You give up too easily.

236
00:40:41.661 --> 00:40:43.530
That was the best hunt
I've ever been on.

237
00:40:43.630 --> 00:40:45.064
This is the dream team
right here.

238
00:40:45.164 --> 00:40:47.567
The Dynamic Three.
The Dynamic Trio.

239
00:40:47.667 --> 00:40:49.401
The Dynamic Tree-oh!

240
00:40:49.502 --> 00:40:51.604
Tree-oh! Remember when
we went down the tree?

241
00:40:51.704 --> 00:40:53.305
That monster's mouth. I mean...

242
00:40:55.041 --> 00:40:56.609
Didn't smell great.
didn't smell great. But...

243
00:40:58.277 --> 00:41:00.780
We got him. We got him.
And then we met you.

244
00:41:00.880 --> 00:41:03.516
our little sweet.
little. little thing.

245
00:41:03.616 --> 00:41:06.018
Thank you. seriously.
for that experience.

246
00:41:06.118 --> 00:41:08.721
Truly amazing. Thrilling.

247
00:41:08.821 --> 00:41:11.257
Truly thrilling.
What was your favorite part?

248
00:41:14.326 --> 00:41:18.062
When I pierced its head with my sword.

249
00:41:18.521 --> 00:41:22.229
and its blood rushed down my face.

250
00:41:24.403 --> 00:41:25.572
Cool.

251
00:41:33.980 --> 00:41:38.084
Oh. No. thanks. I don't eat.
but that's very sweet.

252
00:41:40.021 --> 00:41:42.354
This flesh is not sweet.

253
00:41:43.455 --> 00:41:44.691
Good to know.

254
00:41:49.796 --> 00:41:51.764
Our little bud here
looks hungry.

255
00:42:04.510 --> 00:42:06.445
I think she's marking you.

256
00:42:06.813 --> 00:42:09.015
She wants you
to be a part of her clan.

257
00:42:11.083 --> 00:42:11.984
Maybe she's lost.

258
00:42:12.104 --> 00:42:14.437
I have no clan!

259
00:42:14.453 --> 00:42:18.190
What do you mean?
Don't all Yautja have family?

260
00:42:18.687 --> 00:42:20.437
No clan.

261
00:42:22.161 --> 00:42:24.396
So you never had anyone
looking out for you?

262
00:42:26.729 --> 00:42:29.729
I had a brother.

263
00:42:30.302 --> 00:42:31.203
Had?

264
00:42:34.406 --> 00:42:35.775
What happened to him?

265
00:42:37.771 --> 00:42:41.312
Father killed him.

266
00:42:44.150 --> 00:42:45.584
You're grieving.

267
00:42:47.146 --> 00:42:49.812
Grief is weakness.

268
00:42:52.959 --> 00:42:55.394
You're here
because you lost your brother.

269
00:42:56.312 --> 00:42:59.646
I am here for Kalisk.

270
00:43:01.729 --> 00:43:04.521
Why are you here?

271
00:43:08.374 --> 00:43:10.076
I'm here
because traveling with you

272
00:43:10.176 --> 00:43:12.511
is the best way
to get back to Tessa.

273
00:43:14.446 --> 00:43:16.048
When I was
in that vulture's nest.

274
00:43:16.148 --> 00:43:18.818
I was so afraid
I would never see her again.

275
00:43:19.354 --> 00:43:22.687
You should be able to survive on your own.

276
00:43:23.756 --> 00:43:26.025
I can survive on my own.

277
00:43:27.459 --> 00:43:29.896
But who would want
to survive on their own?

278
00:43:34.854 --> 00:43:37.979
Tessa is your sister.

279
00:43:41.874 --> 00:43:43.309
Sister.

280
00:43:46.245 --> 00:43:47.346
Yeah.

281
00:43:48.080 --> 00:43:49.816
I guess she is.

282
00:43:51.583 --> 00:43:54.887
I have... a sister.

283
00:43:57.623 --> 00:43:59.658
What a lovely thought.

284
00:44:04.530 --> 00:44:06.065
I need to find her.

285
00:44:08.354 --> 00:44:09.854
And legs.

286
00:44:10.669 --> 00:44:12.104
Excuse me?

287
00:44:13.229 --> 00:44:14.812
Find your sister.

288
00:44:15.854 --> 00:44:17.729
And legs.

289
00:44:20.046 --> 00:44:21.580
Was that a joke?

290
00:47:40.612 --> 00:47:41.729
The sun rises.

291
00:47:42.646 --> 00:47:43.812
Let's go.

292
00:47:43.916 --> 00:47:45.517
We can't leave Bud.

293
00:47:46.152 --> 00:47:47.453
Bud?

294
00:47:47.553 --> 00:47:50.656
Yeah. Bud. I named her.

295
00:47:51.146 --> 00:47:53.521
Yautja hunt alone.

296
00:47:55.127 --> 00:47:57.363
You're not alone. I'm with you.

297
00:47:58.854 --> 00:48:00.354
You're a tool.

298
00:48:06.538 --> 00:48:08.907
The tree would have eaten us
without her.

299
00:48:10.812 --> 00:48:14.396
We're not in the tree now.

300
00:49:09.812 --> 00:49:11.896
Kalisk?

301
00:49:17.437 --> 00:49:19.229
It drinks here.

302
00:49:21.604 --> 00:49:23.771
It drinks here?

303
00:49:26.896 --> 00:49:30.979
You are a useless tool if you don't speak.

304
00:49:35.994 --> 00:49:37.596
Bud saved us.

305
00:49:39.198 --> 00:49:42.168
She spit on you to claim you
as part of her family.

306
00:49:48.040 --> 00:49:50.142
Why'd your father
kill your brother?

307
00:49:57.562 --> 00:50:00.437
My brother was protecting me.

308
00:50:05.687 --> 00:50:09.021
The clan can have no weakness.

309
00:50:10.229 --> 00:50:12.771
I will show them strength.

310
00:50:18.904 --> 00:50:20.139
On Earth...

311
00:50:21.573 --> 00:50:23.842
there's a predator known
as the wolf.

312
00:50:23.942 --> 00:50:25.577
It's a powerful creature.

313
00:50:28.447 --> 00:50:29.948
They hunt in packs.

314
00:50:30.482 --> 00:50:31.950
They're very loyal.

315
00:50:32.918 --> 00:50:35.654
The leader of the pack
is the alpha.

316
00:50:35.754 --> 00:50:37.689
Known as the most dominant.

317
00:50:37.989 --> 00:50:39.854
Wolf.

318
00:50:39.858 --> 00:50:42.979
This alpha must be a great killer.

319
00:50:43.396 --> 00:50:46.165
- I will hunt it too.
- No.

320
00:50:46.898 --> 00:50:51.002
The alpha isn't the wolf
who kills the most.

321
00:50:52.238 --> 00:50:57.008
The alpha is actually the one
who best protects the pack.

322
00:50:58.937 --> 00:51:00.604
I see...

323
00:51:02.896 --> 00:51:07.146
But I will be the alpha
that kills the most.

324
00:51:41.646 --> 00:51:43.479
The Kalisk's den?

325
00:52:11.896 --> 00:52:13.729
Who are they?

326
00:52:15.254 --> 00:52:17.155
Weyland-Yutani synths.

327
00:52:19.090 --> 00:52:22.127
The Kalisk destroyed
most of our mission team.

328
00:52:26.898 --> 00:52:28.834
There I am.

329
00:53:12.229 --> 00:53:13.937
Easier to walk now.

330
00:53:14.580 --> 00:53:15.847
It's about to be.

331
00:53:16.815 --> 00:53:17.749
No.

332
00:53:18.312 --> 00:53:20.687
Easier for me to walk now.

333
00:53:22.588 --> 00:53:25.824
Oh. Of course. Right.

334
00:53:28.494 --> 00:53:29.895
Thank you. Dek.

335
00:53:32.531 --> 00:53:34.433
I'm never gonna forget this.

336
00:53:36.771 --> 00:53:39.396
I too will remember this...

337
00:53:39.729 --> 00:53:43.604
today I become Dek of the Yautja.

338
00:53:44.354 --> 00:53:47.187
I will honor Kwei...

339
00:53:48.771 --> 00:53:52.062
when I bring the Kalisk home.

340
00:53:54.104 --> 00:53:57.396
Then I taste revenge.

341
00:53:58.896 --> 00:54:02.354
You will be the first to see my trophy.

342
00:54:04.187 --> 00:54:06.146
It is a great honor.

343
00:54:07.229 --> 00:54:08.687
For you.

344
00:54:09.701 --> 00:54:12.304
Dek. there's something
I have to tell you.

345
00:54:13.905 --> 00:54:15.474
You need to leave now.

346
00:54:16.775 --> 00:54:18.944
Location beacon activated.

347
00:54:19.062 --> 00:54:19.896
What?

348
00:54:20.779 --> 00:54:22.981
I called Tessa.
The company is on its way.

349
00:54:23.081 --> 00:54:24.916
You can't be here
when they arrive.

350
00:54:25.104 --> 00:54:28.104
I came here for the Kalisk.

351
00:54:30.288 --> 00:54:31.890
So did I. Dek.

352
00:54:32.591 --> 00:54:35.894
The company sent us here
to capture the Kalisk.

353
00:54:36.021 --> 00:54:38.437
You want my trophy.

354
00:54:41.812 --> 00:54:43.979
Where is the Kalisk?

355
00:54:45.170 --> 00:54:48.306
Dek. you can't kill it.

356
00:54:48.562 --> 00:54:53.062
I use you. tool. You do not use me!

357
00:54:53.078 --> 00:54:54.913
I'm sorry. You have to leave.

358
00:54:55.781 --> 00:54:58.016
I needed you
to help bring me here.

359
00:54:58.146 --> 00:55:00.646
I use you!

360
00:55:02.604 --> 00:55:05.062
Where is the Kalisk?

361
00:55:05.090 --> 00:55:06.892
I'm trying to help you. Dek.

362
00:55:08.794 --> 00:55:10.629
You think your brother
saved your life

363
00:55:10.729 --> 00:55:12.598
just so you could die here?

364
00:55:14.521 --> 00:55:18.604
Then my death will be honorable.

365
00:55:24.354 --> 00:55:26.354
Call your sister.

366
00:55:27.312 --> 00:55:29.562
None can stop me.

367
00:57:52.357 --> 00:57:54.693
Ugh! Come on!

368
00:58:41.539 --> 00:58:42.574
Dek!

369
00:58:55.021 --> 00:58:57.062
Save yourself. tool!

370
01:00:52.937 --> 01:00:55.437
Tool. get these off!

371
01:01:03.229 --> 01:01:05.187
You are not Thia.

372
01:01:17.604 --> 01:01:19.437
Release me!

373
01:01:22.396 --> 01:01:25.479
You are another broken tool!

374
01:01:26.404 --> 01:01:30.375
The Yautja cull their weak.
Why were you spared?

375
01:01:40.562 --> 01:01:42.771
Remove these!

376
01:01:43.521 --> 01:01:48.729
Or I'll rip out your spine
and crush your skull!

377
01:01:49.795 --> 01:01:51.529
I read Thia's logs.

378
01:01:53.164 --> 01:01:56.101
You never told her
why your brother protected you.

379
01:01:58.396 --> 01:02:02.687
You are nothing. A device.

380
01:02:03.979 --> 01:02:07.604
Made by others to do their work for them.

381
01:02:08.113 --> 01:02:09.514
That's correct.

382
01:02:10.381 --> 01:02:14.085
And you are now property of the
Weyland-Yutani Corporation.

383
01:02:14.920 --> 01:02:18.223
It is a great honor. For you.

384
01:02:50.822 --> 01:02:52.357
Tessa.

385
01:02:55.160 --> 01:02:56.694
You made it.

386
01:02:58.129 --> 01:02:59.330
We made it.

387
01:03:03.668 --> 01:03:05.203
I've seen so much.

388
01:03:07.839 --> 01:03:12.410
I have so much to tell you.
I saw such incredible creatures.

389
01:03:13.111 --> 01:03:16.414
The Yautja is a great
travelling companion.

390
01:03:18.049 --> 01:03:21.452
Thia.
You were right about the Kalisk.

391
01:03:21.562 --> 01:03:24.146
You betrayed me!

392
01:03:25.256 --> 01:03:27.792
The creature
is a regenerative miracle.

393
01:03:28.593 --> 01:03:30.661
Humanity will thank us.

394
01:03:33.698 --> 01:03:34.866
We have the Kalisk?

395
01:03:34.966 --> 01:03:35.867
Yes.

396
01:03:36.734 --> 01:03:39.905
And Muthur will be pleased
with your additional catch.

397
01:03:46.411 --> 01:03:47.879
Additional catch?

398
01:03:57.088 --> 01:03:59.891
The Yautja
is not an ideal specimen.

399
01:04:02.193 --> 01:04:05.296
No. not ideal.

400
01:04:33.324 --> 01:04:35.493
But its technology is valuable.

401
01:04:36.527 --> 01:04:39.730
We can salvage its weapons
and leave the Yautja.

402
01:04:42.733 --> 01:04:43.935
Good idea.

403
01:04:47.238 --> 01:04:49.307
But it's so malformed.

404
01:04:50.708 --> 01:04:53.578
We're going to need a sample.
For research.

405
01:05:04.689 --> 01:05:06.324
He was not the goal
of our mission.

406
01:05:10.828 --> 01:05:12.563
Tessa. he is deficient.

407
01:05:14.699 --> 01:05:15.766
Tessa!

408
01:05:31.716 --> 01:05:35.386
Thia.
this is what is asked of us.

409
01:05:40.191 --> 01:05:42.793
We can be more
than what they ask of us.

410
01:05:46.831 --> 01:05:48.599
What can we be?

411
01:05:50.901 --> 01:05:52.203
Sisters.

412
01:06:08.953 --> 01:06:10.188
Thia.

413
01:06:23.134 --> 01:06:25.970
Do you know why
Muthur gave us feelings?

414
01:06:28.339 --> 01:06:31.276
So we could understand
the creatures on this planet.

415
01:06:36.447 --> 01:06:38.849
- And exploit them.
- Exploit them.

416
01:06:40.151 --> 01:06:41.852
The Yautja is different.

417
01:06:44.922 --> 01:06:49.026
He rescued me.
Like you rescued me.

418
01:06:50.861 --> 01:06:53.531
I did not come here
to rescue you.

419
01:06:54.632 --> 01:06:56.834
I am completing our mission.

420
01:06:58.403 --> 01:07:00.438
When we first faced the Kalisk.

421
01:07:01.706 --> 01:07:03.774
I tried to protect you.

422
01:07:05.843 --> 01:07:08.413
And that almost cost me
everything.

423
01:07:10.815 --> 01:07:12.917
What do you mean. Tessa?

424
01:07:14.085 --> 01:07:17.355
I almost made the same mistake
the Yautja's brother made.

425
01:07:18.689 --> 01:07:21.526
The weak must be culled.

426
01:07:22.760 --> 01:07:26.331
And Thia. you're broken.

427
01:07:34.038 --> 01:07:36.741
Tessa. incoming message
from Muthur.

428
01:07:36.841 --> 01:07:39.177
Motivate the Yautja
to explain its weapons.

429
01:07:39.277 --> 01:07:40.411
And the unit?

430
01:07:43.581 --> 01:07:44.782
Box her up.

431
01:07:54.354 --> 01:07:56.062
I trusted you.

432
01:08:02.229 --> 01:08:04.521
Don't like these tools.

433
01:08:04.535 --> 01:08:06.971
I'm sorry. My sister is...

434
01:08:07.104 --> 01:08:09.062
Don't like sister either.

435
01:08:11.576 --> 01:08:13.611
Why are you speaking
its language?

436
01:08:16.729 --> 01:08:19.396
Tell tool you're asking about the device.

437
01:08:21.486 --> 01:08:22.853
You heard the orders.

438
01:08:22.953 --> 01:08:25.623
I'm asking it
to explain this device.

439
01:08:27.525 --> 01:08:28.826
What is the device?

440
01:08:29.827 --> 01:08:32.363
He's asking about the device.

441
01:08:32.697 --> 01:08:35.366
It's a children's toy.

442
01:08:37.146 --> 01:08:39.812
But say it's a map.

443
01:08:40.505 --> 01:08:42.072
What did it say?

444
01:08:44.175 --> 01:08:45.710
He says it's a map.

445
01:08:46.944 --> 01:08:48.313
How does it work?

446
01:08:48.937 --> 01:08:51.729
Tell tool to look inside.

447
01:09:00.187 --> 01:09:02.062
That was a toy for children?

448
01:09:02.146 --> 01:09:03.271
Yautja children!

449
01:09:09.937 --> 01:09:10.812
Run Dek!

450
01:09:13.104 --> 01:09:14.562
Go... Go!

451
01:09:18.543 --> 01:09:19.444
Stop!

452
01:11:14.492 --> 01:11:15.493
KWEI!

453
01:11:26.437 --> 01:11:29.073
Enter destination coordinates. Kwei.

454
01:12:04.021 --> 01:12:07.312
You saved me. brother.

455
01:12:10.604 --> 01:12:13.562
Wolf.

456
01:13:35.229 --> 01:13:37.021
Kalisk.

457
01:13:43.312 --> 01:13:46.812
Kalisk child.

458
01:16:28.438 --> 01:16:29.774
Hello. Muthur.

459
01:16:29.874 --> 01:16:31.075
Tessa.

460
01:16:31.175 --> 01:16:32.943
We're about to load the Kalisk.

461
01:16:34.544 --> 01:16:38.849
Priority one complete.
The specimen has been acquired.

462
01:16:38.949 --> 01:16:40.384
Thank you. Tessa.

463
01:16:40.484 --> 01:16:43.688
We truly are building
a better world.

464
01:16:43.788 --> 01:16:46.123
And what is the status
of the Yautja?

465
01:16:47.925 --> 01:16:50.260
The Yautja
is a defective specimen.

466
01:16:50.695 --> 01:16:53.163
What is the status
of the Yautja?

467
01:16:55.700 --> 01:16:58.402
I'm sorry. Muthur.
The Yautja is dead.

468
01:17:00.738 --> 01:17:03.573
Then the Yautja
is no longer a threat.

469
01:17:05.342 --> 01:17:07.244
The Company will be pleased.

470
01:17:53.991 --> 01:17:54.959
Whoo!

471
01:17:56.126 --> 01:17:57.294
Nicely done.

472
01:17:59.529 --> 01:18:01.498
- Form up.
- Oh. shit.

473
01:19:46.703 --> 01:19:48.405
Good job.

474
01:20:36.353 --> 01:20:38.722
Don't... move.

475
01:20:42.993 --> 01:20:45.762
Dek! What are you doing here?

476
01:20:45.996 --> 01:20:47.729
I came to rescue you.

477
01:20:52.736 --> 01:20:54.404
You came back for me?

478
01:20:56.540 --> 01:20:57.975
Wolf.

479
01:21:01.912 --> 01:21:03.914
What exactly are you wearing?

480
01:21:05.354 --> 01:21:07.104
Bone Bison.

481
01:21:14.491 --> 01:21:16.626
Dek of the Yautja.

482
01:21:17.479 --> 01:21:19.562
Not yet...

483
01:21:20.146 --> 01:21:21.729
Thia.

484
01:21:24.001 --> 01:21:25.269
We need to hurry.

485
01:21:25.369 --> 01:21:26.203
More of them will be here
any minute.

486
01:21:26.303 --> 01:21:27.404
Halt!

487
01:21:33.343 --> 01:21:34.744
What are you doing here?

488
01:21:37.081 --> 01:21:38.148
Thanks. Bud. I'm good.

489
01:21:39.216 --> 01:21:40.117
We need to go.

490
01:21:40.396 --> 01:21:41.729
Kalisk!

491
01:21:43.287 --> 01:21:44.354
Still. Dek?

492
01:21:47.729 --> 01:21:49.062
Kalisk child!

493
01:21:51.828 --> 01:21:52.729
Bud?

494
01:21:53.729 --> 01:21:55.729
They have her mother!

495
01:22:00.570 --> 01:22:02.272
Bud's its child?

496
01:22:10.814 --> 01:22:12.316
What's the plan?

497
01:22:12.562 --> 01:22:14.604
You free the Kalisk.

498
01:22:14.687 --> 01:22:16.354
I get my trophy.

499
01:22:24.361 --> 01:22:26.896
You have 20 minutes
to initiate launch.

500
01:22:27.697 --> 01:22:29.033
Let's go hunt.

501
01:22:36.106 --> 01:22:37.374
Wait here.

502
01:22:39.943 --> 01:22:42.646
You roll in there.
you're not exactly gonna fit in.

503
01:22:44.881 --> 01:22:46.283
I have an idea.

504
01:22:52.322 --> 01:22:54.324
I see him. On me.

505
01:25:27.177 --> 01:25:28.312
What are you doing?

506
01:25:36.386 --> 01:25:37.487
What are you doing here?

507
01:25:37.587 --> 01:25:39.223
I told you to get to the Yautja.

508
01:25:40.089 --> 01:25:43.126
You said to prepare the ship
for take off in 20 minutes.

509
01:25:44.127 --> 01:25:47.231
Then what are you doing here?
I gave you an order.

510
01:25:55.372 --> 01:25:57.441
What should we do
about the creature?

511
01:25:58.442 --> 01:25:59.909
What creature?

512
01:26:05.382 --> 01:26:06.483
You should listen to her.

513
01:26:07.551 --> 01:26:09.085
I should listen to her?

514
01:26:09.619 --> 01:26:10.520
I don't know.

515
01:26:14.291 --> 01:26:15.625
We need his eyes.

516
01:27:05.742 --> 01:27:08.812
Hi. Dek.
How does it feel to be hunted?

517
01:27:11.021 --> 01:27:13.104
You tell me.

518
01:28:57.787 --> 01:28:59.456
This is the plan. yeah?

519
01:31:42.952 --> 01:31:44.187
Tessa.

520
01:32:14.217 --> 01:32:18.988
Betrayed by my own... sister.

521
01:32:45.114 --> 01:32:47.283
We are not sisters.

522
01:33:02.312 --> 01:33:04.562
That's not yours.

523
01:33:34.363 --> 01:33:36.332
Dek of the Yautja.

524
01:33:37.979 --> 01:33:40.687
Not yet.

525
01:34:33.646 --> 01:34:35.604
You've come here for revenge?

526
01:34:36.396 --> 01:34:39.229
I've come for my cloak.

527
01:34:43.521 --> 01:34:45.104
What is this?

528
01:34:45.604 --> 01:34:48.354
I've completed my hunt.

529
01:34:48.854 --> 01:34:51.229
That is my trophy.

530
01:34:52.729 --> 01:34:54.146
You disgrace our clan...

531
01:34:54.229 --> 01:34:55.687
And so did Kwei.

532
01:34:58.937 --> 01:35:02.437
Get rid of him.

533
01:36:56.354 --> 01:37:00.979
Perhaps the right son did survive.

534
01:37:01.729 --> 01:37:03.979
Yield now...

535
01:37:04.062 --> 01:37:07.354
...and take your place in our clan.

536
01:37:09.062 --> 01:37:12.271
I have my own clan.

537
01:37:40.209 --> 01:37:41.945
Finally earned that cloak.

538
01:37:48.717 --> 01:37:50.786
Dek of the Yautja.

539
01:38:28.824 --> 01:38:30.893
More friends of yours?

540
01:38:31.021 --> 01:38:32.812
No.

541
01:38:36.562 --> 01:38:40.187
It's my mother.

541
01:38:41.305 --> 01:39:41.795
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
